http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Thiruvananthapuram/Career-counselling-today/article14013420.ece

A career guidance meet by GITAM University and The Hindu School Edition will be held at Panchayat Association Hall, Waterworks Compound, Vellayambalam, on Friday.The meet that will begin at 10.30 a.m. aims at creating awareness among intermediate students of professional and general higher education courses, selection of engineering branches and institutes.Experts will deal with ways to choose best engineering, pharmacy or architecture colleges. Lectures on science programmes, opportunities in science, research, and national-level tests will be delivered. The meet will also focus on management education, particularly at the undergraduate level. The entry is free.